      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Alessandro Scotti</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"https://walkofmind.com/programming/chess/ccc2005.htm\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/UbaldoAlessandro.jpg/300px-UbaldoAlessandro.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/UbaldoAlessandro.jpg/450px-UbaldoAlessandro.jpg 1.5x, /images/e/e5/UbaldoAlessandro.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:UbaldoAlessandro.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/Ubaldo_Andrea_Farina\" title=\"Ubaldo Andrea Farina\">Ubaldo Andrea Farina</a> and Alessandro Scotti <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Alessandro Scotti</b>,<br />\nan Italian software developer and computer chess programmer. He is author of the chess engines <a href=\"/Kiwi\" title=\"Kiwi\">Kiwi</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> \nand <a href=\"/Hamsters\" title=\"Hamsters\">Hamsters</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. Alessandro also tinkered with the <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a> source code, and was able to add a few new features to it <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alessandro_Scotti&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alessandro_Scotti&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=858\">Perpetual check</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alessandro Scotti</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, December 03, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">Repetitions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=1855\">Side effects of transposition tables</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alessandro Scotti</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, March 04, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=3110\">Piece-list representation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alessandro Scotti</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, July 17, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Piece-Lists\" title=\"Piece-Lists\">Piece-Lists</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=489960\">Outside passer and candidate passer: definition wanted!&#160;:-)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alessandro Scotti</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 27, 2006&#160;» <a href=\"/Outside_Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Outside Passed Pawn\">Outside Passed Pawn</a>, <a href=\"/Candidate_Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Candidate Passed Pawn\">Candidate Passed Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=13166\">Material imbalance evaluation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alessandro Scotti</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 16, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">Material</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=18240\">Evaluation of material imbalance (a Rybka secret?)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alessandro Scotti</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 06, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">Material</a>, <a href=\"/Rybka\" title=\"Rybka\">Rybka</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=18345\">LMR: history or not?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alessandro Scotti</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 13, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alessandro_Scotti&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://walkofmind.com/index.html\">Walk Of Mind</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://walkofmind.com/homepage/homepage.htm\">Alessandro Scotti Personal Homepage</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://walkofmind.com/programming/programming.htm\">Alessandro Scotti's Computer Programming Site</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://walkofmind.com/programming/chess/chess.htm\">Alessandro Scotti's Computer Chess Site</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://walkofmind.com/programming/chess/winboard_x.htm\">Tinkering with Winboard...</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://walkofmind.com/programming/chess/xboard.htm\">Winboard/XBoard UML state diagram</a></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alessandro_Scotti&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://walkofmind.com/programming/chess/ccc2005.htm\">Computer Chess Cup 2005</a> by Alessandro Scotti, <a href=\"/CCC_2005\" title=\"CCC 2005\">CCC 2005</a> </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://walkofmind.com/programming/chess/chess.htm\">Alessandro Scotti's Computer Chess Site</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://walkofmind.com/programming/chess/hamsters.htm\">Hamsters homepage</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://walkofmind.com/programming/chess/winboard_x.htm\">Tinkering with Winboard...</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301092705\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.014 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.016 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 75/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 166/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:5523-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301092705 and revision id 12056\n -->\n"
